high_descs: Go straight and turn right to the desk ahead.
Pick up the butter knife that is against the wall, to the left of the mango.
Go to the drawers immediately to the right.
Place the butter knife into the drawer.
Turn left back to the desk where you got the knife.
Pick up the butter knife that is directly next to the plate.
Go back to the drawers you put the first knife in.
Place the second butter knife into the drawers.
anns.task_desc: Place two butter knives into a drawer.

high_descs: Go straight and turn to the desk to your right.
Pick up the butter knife on the desk.
Go to the drawer to your right.
Put the butter knife in the middle drawer.
Turn around and go to the plate on the desk.
Pick up the butter knife on the desk.
Turn right and go to the drawer.
Put the butter knife in the middle drawer.
anns.task_desc: To put the butter knives in the drawer.

high_descs: Go straight and turn right towards the desk.
Pick up one butter knife out of two from the desk.
Turn right and walk side to the desk.
Put the butter knife in the middle rack of the drawer.
Turn back, walk, and turn right towards the desk.
Pick up the second butter knife from the desk.
Turn right and walk side to the desk.
Put the second butter knife in the middle rack of the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two butter knives in the drawer.
